						               													<description>A Hero Will Rise to Face the Agents of Darkness.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Spriggan model is unique to KS, but the deck used is not.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Spriggan uses spells. It has two types of spells: attacking spells that awaken nature to attack the darkness like Bee Swarm or Gaia's embrace, and spells that equip the Spriggan with temporary items: like Oaken Armor and Willow's Kiss.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The equip spells provide the Spriggan with items it can equip and use with it's more standard attack cards. These items have limited hit points or do limited Blood. When they are spent, the item goes away.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There will be only one miniature for the Spriggan. We consider it genderless.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
